\begin_inset Formula $\nu_{0}=4.74\times10^{14}$
\end_inset

 Hz and 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta\nu=\frac{c}{2L}=1.50\times10^{9}$
\end_inset

 Hz.
 Figure 1 shows a plot of (10) after normalization, using these values,
 and 
\begin_inset Formula $a=1$
\end_inset

